					no_cancel_button => 1,
					one_column => 1,
					} &>
</td></tr>
<tr><td class="xsm" colspan="2">
<br>
Only image file types are allowed (specifically: .jpg, .jpeg, .bmp, .png, or .gif). Multiple files can be selected and imported at one time. To select multiple files while browsing, hold down the 'Ctrl' button on your keyboard. Note that the maximum allowed file size is 4 megabytes.<br><br>
File names must be in one of the following 3 formats: <br><br> 
lastname.firstname (e.g. Smith.John.jpg) <BR> 
lastname.firstinitial (e.g. Smith.J.jpg) <BR>
UTLN (e.g. jsmith01.jpg) <BR><br>
The last convention, UTLN, is the preferred format.<br> 

<br>
</td></tr>
